    <lb n="9"/><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὅτι οὐκ </supplied><choice><corr><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ὀ</supplied>κνήσεις</corr><sic><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">κ</unclear>νησις</sic></choice> ἐν οἷς σοι ἐπιστέλλω. μόνον 

